=======
LEGEND
=======

. = Background
P = Background and Player
# = Background and Wall
x = Background and Monster

BFS1 = BFS1U or BFS1D or BFS1L or BFS1R
BFS2 = BFS2U or BFS2D or BFS2L or BFS2R
BFS  = BFS1 or BFS2

BFSU = BFS1U or BFS2U
BFSD = BFS1D or BFS2D
BFSL = BFS1L or BFS2L
BFSR = BFS1R or BFS2R

