======
RULES
======
[ action Player] -> win

left  [ left  Player | no Wall no Monster ] -> [ | Player ]
right [ right Player | no Wall no Monster ] -> [ | Player ]
up    [ up    Player | no Wall no Monster ] -> [ | Player ]
down  [ down  Player | no Wall no Monster ] -> [ | Player ]

[ Player ] -> [ stationary Player ]

[BFS] -> []
[ Player ] -> [ Player random BFS1U ]

startloop

  down [ no BFS2 no BFS1 no Wall no Player | BFS1 no Monster ] -> [ BFS2D | BFS1 ]
  up   [ no BFS2 no BFS1 no Wall no Player | BFS1 no Monster ] -> [ BFS2U | BFS1 ]
  right[ no BFS2 no BFS1 no Wall no Player | BFS1 no Monster ] -> [ BFS2R | BFS1 ]
  left [ no BFS2 no BFS1 no Wall no Player | BFS1 no Monster ] -> [ BFS2L | BFS1 ]

  down [ no BFS2 no BFS1 no Wall no Player | BFS2 no Monster ] -> [ BFS1D | BFS2 ]
  up   [ no BFS2 no BFS1 no Wall no Player | BFS2 no Monster ] -> [ BFS1U | BFS2 ]
  right[ no BFS2 no BFS1 no Wall no Player | BFS2 no Monster ] -> [ BFS1R | BFS2 ]
  left [ no BFS2 no BFS1 no Wall no Player | BFS2 no Monster ] -> [ BFS1L | BFS2 ]


endloop

[ BFSU Monster ] -> [ up    Monster ]
[ BFSD Monster ] -> [ down  Monster ]
[ BFSL Monster ] -> [ left  Monster ]
[ BFSR Monster ] -> [ right Monster ]

late [ Monster | Player ] -> [ Monster | ] 




